 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/atombios_encoders.c    | 14 --------------
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/amdgpu_dm/amdgpu_dm.c | 15 +--------------
 4 files changed, 1 insertion(+), 38 deletions(-)

